# Core Architecture

- Treat `docs/ADR/ADR-001.md`, `docs/ADR/ADR-002.md`, and `docs/ADR/ADR-003.md` as the source of truth.
- Keep `ControlSystemConfig` JSON-ready and resolve runtime instances through registries.
- Preserve the `control` / `runtime` split; never move domain truth into runtime metadata.
- Keep checkpointed state serializable and bounded-memory aware.
- Forbid destructive side effects when `simulation` is true.
